#+title: Metaphase
#+author: Paul Gerald D. Pare
#+date: August 23, 2023

* Definition
- Also called "_change phase_".
- All the chromosomes are aligned in a plane called the /metaphase plate/ or the
  /equatorial plane/
- All of the chromosomes are maximally condensed.
